00:15:46,904 --> 00:15:49,907
‎只能走正道的话 路上的用时得翻倍
It's gonna take me twice as long
if I can only use the real lanes.

325
00:15:49,990 --> 00:15:52,242
‎-好的 妈妈 爱你
‎-爱你
-Okay, Mom. Love you.
-Love you.

326
00:15:53,661 --> 00:15:55,746
‎-很高兴认识你 奥兹
‎-我也一样
-Nice to meet you, Ozzie.
-You too.

327
00:15:55,829 --> 00:15:57,748
‎看来莉亚的美貌是随了妈妈
I can see where Leia gets her good looks.

328
00:15:57,831 --> 00:15:59,833
‎你真讨人喜欢
Oh! You're a little charmer.

329
00:16:00,793 --> 00:16:02,211
‎你俩确定不会发生关系？
You sure you aren't gonna have sex?

330
00:16:02,294 --> 00:16:04,046
‎-确定
‎-绝对的
-Positive.
-A million percent.

331
00:16:06,674 --> 00:16:09,051
‎按下回车键 就能登录邮箱了
Just hit enter
and you'll be signed in to your email.

332
00:16:09,134 --> 00:16:11,470
[rhythmic mouth noises]

333
00:16:11,553 --> 00:16:13,722
‎你有邮件
‎我的天 我收到了邮件 太刺激了
-[male voice] <i>You've got mail.</i>
-Oh my God, I've got mail.

334
00:16:13,806 --> 00:16:15,724
‎我的天 我收到了邮件 太刺激了
Oh! This is thrilling.

335
00:16:15,808 --> 00:16:18,352
‎虽说我生过娃 但这个也相当刺激
I mean, I've had kids,
but this is right up there.

336
00:16:19,144 --> 00:16:20,813
‎其实 邮件是我发的
Actually, that's from me.

337
00:16:21,313 --> 00:16:24,525
‎我有话一直想跟你说 打开吧
There's something I've been trying
to tell you, so go ahead and open it.

338
00:16:24,608 --> 00:16:25,693
Oh?

339
00:16:25,776 --> 00:16:26,986
‎好
Okay.

340
00:16:27,861 --> 00:16:30,322
‎双击一下小邮箱
Double-click on the little mailbox.

341
00:16:32,074 --> 00:16:33,367
‎天啊
Oh dear.

342
00:16:33,450 --> 00:16:35,285
‎跑哪儿去了？
Where did it go?

343
00:16:35,995 --> 00:16:36,996
‎就在这里
It's right there.

344
00:16:38,247 --> 00:16:39,081
Oh.

345
00:16:39,164 --> 00:16:40,332
‎点啊点
-Click-click!
-[mouse clicks]

346
00:16:40,416 --> 00:16:42,501
‎不 是角落里的小邮箱
No. The little box in the corner.

347
00:16:43,085 --> 00:16:44,837
‎-全没了
‎-在这后面
-The whole thing is gone.
-It's behind there.

348
00:16:44,920 --> 00:16:46,338
‎-在啥后面？
‎-那个窗口
-Behind where?
-That window.

349
00:16:46,422 --> 00:16:48,590
[loud computer chime]

350
00:16:48,674 --> 00:16:49,675
[Ozzie huffs]

351
00:16:51,635 --> 00:16:52,845
‎重启 那…
Restarting. So…

352
00:16:55,014 --> 00:16:56,473
‎我们得等五分钟
We have about five minutes.

353
00:16:57,850 --> 00:16:58,809
[sighs]

354
00:16:58,892 --> 00:16:59,893
‎算了
Forget it.

355
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:02,229
‎福尔曼太太
Mrs. Forman.

356
00:17:03,105 --> 00:17:03,939
‎我是同性恋
I'm gay.

357
00:17:05,232 --> 00:17:07,985
‎我知道很久了 现在想告诉你
I've known for a while now,
and I wanted you to know.

358
00:17:08,068 --> 00:17:10,738
‎我还有个叫艾蒂安的男友
‎他住在加拿大
I even have a boyfriend,
Etienne, who lives in Canada.

359
00:17:12,406 --> 00:17:14,241
‎我不知道对此该作何感想
Well, I don't know how I feel about this.

360
00:17:14,992 --> 00:17:15,826
Oh.

361
00:17:16,410 --> 00:17:19,371
‎我朋友莎朗就嫁了一个加国人
‎他把莎朗的丰田旅行车偷跑了
My friend Sharon married a Canadian man,

362
00:17:19,455 --> 00:17:22,041
‎我朋友莎朗就嫁了一个加国人
‎他把莎朗的丰田旅行车偷跑了
and he made off with her Toyota wagon.

363
00:17:22,124 --> 00:17:26,086
‎车里还放着她猫咪的骨灰
‎可把她坑惨了
And her cat's ashes were in there,
and she is a mess.

364
00:17:28,213 --> 00:17:30,632
‎但…你不介意我是同性恋吗？
But… you're okay with me being gay?

365
00:17:30,716 --> 00:17:32,092
‎当然不介意
Well, of course I am.

366
00:17:33,260 --> 00:17:36,430
‎好孩子 到这儿来
Oh, sweet boy, get in here.

367
00:17:39,224 --> 00:17:42,227
‎你让我觉得自己很特别
You just made me feel really special.

368
00:17:43,353 --> 00:17:44,396
[chuckles softly]

369
00:17:47,608 --> 00:17:49,193
[inhales, exhales sharply]

370
00:17:50,360 --> 00:17:52,696
‎这就是你帮我装电脑的原因吗？
Is that why you helped me
with the computer?

371
00:17:53,447 --> 00:17:55,532
‎不 是因为我喜欢
No, I did it because I loved it.

372
00:17:56,408 --> 00:17:58,327
[laughs giddily]

373
00:17:59,912 --> 00:18:03,040
[rock music playing]

374
00:18:07,002 --> 00:18:09,755
‎那个…昨天 是吧？
So… yesterday, huh?

375
00:18:10,631 --> 00:18:11,882
‎真没想到
Very unexpected.

376
00:18:13,175 --> 00:18:14,009
‎我们…？
Did we…?

377
00:18:14,676 --> 00:18:16,011
‎玩爽了没？必须的 两回呢
Have fun? Yeah.

378
00:18:16,553 --> 00:18:17,554
‎玩爽了没？必须的 两回呢
We did.

379
00:18:18,180 --> 00:18:19,014
‎玩爽了没？必须的 两回呢
Twice.

380
00:18:20,390 --> 00:18:22,601
‎-还是别提这件事了
‎-秘密带进坟墓里
-Let's never talk about this again.
-Secret dies with me.

381
00:18:24,478 --> 00:18:25,729
‎妮可 坐这儿吧
Sit here, Nik.

382
00:18:25,813 --> 00:18:28,023
‎我要拿这片生菜去喂山羊
I'm gonna take this lettuce
out to my goat.

383
00:18:28,982 --> 00:18:29,817
‎你不会吧
You did not.

384
00:18:29,900 --> 00:18:31,860
‎不要钱的呀
It was free, Nik!

385
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:34,822
‎你现在是山羊妈妈了
You're a goat's mommy now.

386
00:18:35,447 --> 00:18:36,824
‎好吧 真可爱
Okay, that's cute.

387
00:18:38,826 --> 00:18:41,453
‎好了 第七步搞定 接下来呢？
So, step seven is in the books.
What's next?

388
00:18:41,537 --> 00:18:42,746
‎-我偷了辆车
‎-真的吗？
-I steal a car.
-Really?

389
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:44,540
‎没有 我告诉了我的儿科医生
No, I tell my pediatrician.

390
00:18:46,917 --> 00:18:49,002
‎天啊 杰伊进来了
Oh God. Jay just walked in.

391
00:18:49,086 --> 00:18:50,796
‎还穿着那件小T恤
He's wearing that tiny T-shirt.

392
00:18:52,131 --> 00:18:54,550
‎我的天啊 他累的时候越发帅了
Oh my God. He's even hotter
when he's tired.

393
00:18:55,968 --> 00:18:57,761
‎你说这友情牌 我还要打多久？
How long do I keep
this friend thing going?

394
00:18:57,845 --> 00:19:00,347
‎难说 是你出了这不着调的主意
I don't know. It was your crazy-ass idea.

395
00:19:02,099 --> 00:19:03,183
‎去找他谈谈就是了
Just go talk to him.

396
00:19:03,267 --> 00:19:04,434
‎我该怎么说？
What am I supposed to do?

397
00:19:04,518 --> 00:19:07,604
‎在番茄酱跟前
‎对他说出我的爱？太可怕了
Profess my love to him in front of
the ketchup pump? That's so scary.

398
00:19:07,688 --> 00:19:10,607
‎我刚跟你奶奶出柜
‎你连跟知道你心意的男生说出心意
I just came out to your grandma.
You can tell a guy who knows you like him

399
00:19:10,691 --> 00:19:11,525
‎都不敢哇
that you like him.

400
00:19:14,778 --> 00:19:17,197
‎-那是妮基的发箍吗？
‎-什么？
-Is that Nikki's scrunchie?
-What?!

401
00:19:17,698 --> 00:19:18,866
‎不是
No. [nervous chuckle]

402
00:19:19,575 --> 00:19:20,492
‎嘿
Hey.

403
00:19:21,243 --> 00:19:22,119
‎嗨
Hey.

404
00:19:22,202 --> 00:19:25,664
‎还记得那天晚上
‎我说只想跟你做朋友吗？
Um, so you know how the other night
I said I just wanted to be friends?

405
00:19:25,747 --> 00:19:28,125
‎是啊 真意外 还是不好受那种
Yeah. That was a surprise,
and not the fun kind.

406
00:19:29,710 --> 00:19:31,962
‎那我接下来要说的 你肯定爱听
Well, then you're gonna like
what I'm about to say.

407
00:19:32,045 --> 00:19:33,797
‎抱歉 停车费了好大功夫
Sorry. It took me forever to park.

408
00:19:33,881 --> 00:19:36,091
‎你的朋友在停车场追着一只山羊乱跑
Your friend is chasing a goat
around the parking lot

409
00:19:36,175 --> 00:19:37,384
‎还有一个女生冲他吼叫
while some girl yells at him.

410
00:19:38,886 --> 00:19:40,971
‎咱们第一次约会至少有件趣事
At least we'll have a story
for our first date.

411
00:19:43,557 --> 00:19:45,017
‎赛琳娜 这是我朋友莉亚
Oh, Serena, this is my friend Leia.

412
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:46,185
‎你好 朋友
Howdy, friend!

413
00:19:48,729 --> 00:19:52,107
‎我就是…来打点番茄酱
I was, uh, just getting some ketchup
from the big ol' pump.

414
00:19:57,362 --> 00:19:58,363
‎雷德？
Red?

415
00:20:01,241 --> 00:20:02,367
‎你在做什么？
What are you doing?

416
00:20:03,577 --> 00:20:04,536
Uh…

417
00:20:04,620 --> 00:20:06,163
‎没什么 回去睡觉吧
Nothing. Go back to bed.

418
00:20:06,872 --> 00:20:09,249
‎雷德福尔曼 你把手拿开
Red Forman, move your hands.

419
00:20:09,333 --> 00:20:10,918
[Red groans]

420
00:20:15,672 --> 00:20:17,007
‎这是拉蔻儿薇芝？
Is that Raquel Welch?

421
00:20:21,929 --> 00:20:23,722
‎还真是！
[gasps] It is!

422
00:20:25,807 --> 00:20:26,808
‎雷德福尔曼
Red Forman.

423
00:20:28,602 --> 00:20:32,022
‎你用新电脑了 我真高兴
I am so happy
you're using the new computer!

424
00:20:33,565 --> 00:20:35,609
‎好了 帮我找找柯克道格拉斯的
Now, find me one of Kirk Douglas.

425
00:20:36,693 --> 00:20:37,611
[Red clears throat]

426
00:20:37,694 --> 00:20:40,113
‎-穿角斗士装那种
‎-好
-In his gladiator outfit.
-Oh… Okay…

427
00:20:41,573 --> 00:20:42,616
‎尽情享受吧
Have at it.

428
00:20:44,326 --> 00:20:45,494
[clicking mouse]

429
00:20:45,577 --> 00:20:46,662
[loud computer chime]

430
00:20:46,745 --> 00:20:47,871
‎重启中
Restarting.

431
00:20:50,165 --> 00:20:53,085
[rock music playing]

432
00:21:26,618 --> 00:21:30,122
‎字幕翻译：Zeo Niu

